> https://github.com/kdevkr/spring-demo-ajax   .

### JQuery.ajax

### Axios
Axios   VueJS   JQuery.ajax    HTTP . 

#### Axios.post
```js
const $data = new FormData();
$data.append('files', $file);
$data.append('files', $file);

// Send a POST request
axios({
  method: 'post',
  url: $url,
  data: $data,
  headers: {
    'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data'
  }
});

// Request method aliases
axios.post($url, $data, {
    headers: {
      'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data'
    }
})
```

## 
- [Spring-Demo-JQuery-Ajax](https://github.com/kdevkr/spring-demo-ajax)
- [How to post a file from a form with Axios](https://stackoverflow.com/a/43014086)

